<h2> Notes </h2>

<p>
<strong>@HI{{daga}}</strong> is not often used in speech, but if it is it is always followed by @HI{{ne}}. Usually it is replaced in speech by
@HI{{keredomo}} or @HI{{demo}}.
</p>

<p>
<strong>@HI{{daga}}</strong> is always used as a sentence-initial conjunction.
</p>

